							<p>
				What the words <q>per</q> and <q>cent</q> mean in the word <q>percent.</q>
			</p>
				</li>

				<li>
							<p>
				How to convert a fraction or decimal to a percent?
			</p>
				</li>

				<li>
							<p>
				How to convert a percent to a decimal?
			</p>
				</li>

				<li>
							<p>
				How to calculate a percentage of a number?
